10.title: deploy
10.query:
timeseries deployment = max(`devplatform.sam-pipelines.deployment`), 
  by: { `end-time-utc` }, 
  filter: { (`sam-stack-name` == "core-back-build") AND (stage == "deploy") }
| fieldsAdd lastSuccess = if(arrayLast(deployment) == 1, "true", else: "false")
| sort `end-time-utc` desc
| limit 1
